24:10.640 --> 24:12.110
.. under ten people.

24:12.160 --> 24:14.870
As in, fewer than ten, not people
who are under ten, obviously.

24:14.920 --> 24:17.350
That's a completely
different thing. But, um...

24:17.400 --> 24:20.070
I mean, I've only really ever
done the missionary position.

