mother of your children.

25:20.720 --> 25:22.630
No, I'm telling the truth.

25:22.680 --> 25:24.270
But I'm glad I can.

25:24.320 --> 25:27.640
Because, honest to my heart,
Hetty's a wonderful person...

25:28.920 --> 25:30.840
