26:07.520 --> 26:09.230
"Great, now she's got an excuse."

26:09.280 --> 26:11.870
- Oh, we are so fucked.
- And of course, she particularly didn't like it

26:11.920 --> 26:13.870
- that Deanna was half black.
- Racial aggravation.

26:13.920 --> 26:16.750
That's another five months. I'm
never listening to you again.

26:16.800 --> 26:19.700
- Joint decision.
- Sunny and optimistic. Bunch of bollocks.

