27:07.480 --> 27:09.080
You're not even a Buddhist, are you?

27:11.720 --> 27:13.190
But Hetty's a nasty woman.

27:13.240 --> 27:15.440
You can put a dress on
her, it won't change that.

27:16.640 --> 27:18.270
The bad shit we do lingers, brother.

27:18.320 --> 27:20.080
